!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
!!!! Waave needs ffmpeg shared libraries !!!!
!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
-> comfigure ffmpeg with --enable-shared
-> for ffmpeg-0.5 configure ffmpeg with --enable-shared --enable-swscale 

-----------------
EXEMPLE PROGRAMS
-----------------
Exemple programs can be found in the test/ folder.
-> waaveplayer12.c for sdl 1.2
-> waaveplayer20.c for sdl 2.0

compile with :

gcc -g `sdl-config --cflags` waaveplayer12.c -o waaveplayer12 `sdl-config --libs` -lwaave

-------------
DOCUMENTATION
-------------
To build the documentation use the doxygen command.
